内部有想陈旧了，应该再装修一下', '2024-02-11', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''卫生状况'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232z12000d6if1af5C0E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230r12000d6ikgkj3B99_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236012000d6iw0uh406A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '非常满意，很棒的旅程！', '非常满意，很棒的旅程！', '2024-05-27', 5, '[''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231y12000e6ppugc6A1E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234812000e6pi23z52AA_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233b12000e6p7m1mC0CE_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '房间非常好，大厅富丽堂皇，但是内部并没有那么富丽堂皇，服务也还可以', '房间非常好，大厅富丽堂皇，但是内部并没有那么富丽堂皇，服务也还可以
