下次再去住试试看，挺好的??????????', '2023-10-09', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''卫生状况'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232h12000cd1ve1cEBD4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236d12000cd1wwsz336D_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230912000cd1ygjr102A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '环境真的非常好，有山有水又很安静，房间也非常好，刚从广州的花园酒店离开来到这里，', '环境真的非常好，有山有水又很安静，房间也非常好，刚从广州的花园酒店离开来到这里，房间面积，设师，卫生，服务都不比花园酒店差，值得来', '2023-10-05', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''安静程度'', ''卫生状况'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236a12000cc4uajq70E3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231r12000cc4ubuy244A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233l12000cc4ubw57449_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店的环境不错，但是修路他们不安排里面的房间也不提醒你有这样的情况， 太吵了', '酒店的环境不错，但是修路他们不安排里面的房间也不提醒你有这样的情况， 太吵了', '2023-11-20', 2, '[''安静程度'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/023563234d9x3otio3E65_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '广州花园酒店，是我在全国住过众多酒店，唯一一个还想下次来入住的酒店，虽然酒店已经', '广州花园酒店，是我在全国住过众多酒店，唯一一个还想下次来入住的酒店，虽然酒店已经有30年的历史，但酒店整体从环境到服务，没有一个地方让人挑出毛病的，服务非常体贴入微，下次来广州一定还会选择花园酒店，酒店环境真的很美！', '2023-08-12', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''前台服务'', ''客房服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236j12000bw8k7hc6EE0_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231h12000bw8r9hi3B79_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235312000bw8h30b0AB4_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234p12000bw8lxqg5D63_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '虽然酒店历史悠久，但整体环境、装潢一点也不陈旧。工作人员都很热情，特别是泳池边的', '虽然酒店历史悠久，但整体环境、装潢一点也不陈旧。工作人员都很热情，特别是泳池边的几位工作人员，一直贴身守护着小孩子，点个大大的??', '2023-10-04', 5, '[''公共设施'', ''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234712000cbopqzh35D3_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233p12000cbopi86F466_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236a12000cboq53p239A_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '方便很干净.很舒服.这个大床说的我好开心.本来打算住一晚体验下.换别的酒店.结果', '方便很干净.很舒服.这个大床说的我好开心.本来打算住一晚体验下.换别的酒店.结果连着自己了好几天目前还在酒店住.停车也很方便.是免费的.整体来说环境好.舒服方便.', '2023-09-07', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''卫生状况'', ''公共设施'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235j12000c30xrrj927B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230t12000c30n9vi1B61_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0231v12000c30sgd0E055_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235i12000c30r6vyBA5E_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235q12000c31077qB586_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '很棒的住宿体验，服务很好，谢谢前台小钟送的礼物', '很棒的住宿体验，服务很好，谢谢前台小钟送的礼物', '2024-01-17', 5, '[''前台服务'', ''整体满意度'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232x12000cyhtfsp50B5_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0232a12000cyhtqua33BD_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '酒店很大很漂亮，食店都已有六间，服务也很好，环境与空气都很好，我俩很满意。???', '酒店很大很漂亮，食店都已有六间，服务也很好，环境与空气都很好，我俩很满意。??????????', '2023-09-14', 5, '[''整体满意度'', ''餐饮设施'', ''前台服务'']', '["[ \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0234l12000c4v8n8s1EBF_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0235g12000c4valk0AB3F_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236b12000c4vao3qAA1B_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236912000c4vbvjm1A03_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230612000c4vaef38DF2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230z12000c4va66eCCC2_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0236912000c4vbpgp3112_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0233o12000c4vanjy0209_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\", \"https://dimg04.c-ctrip.com/images/0230612000c4v8dcjAF4C_R_150_150_R5_Q70_D.jpg\" ]"]'); INSERT INTO comments (hotel_name, location, reviewer_name, review_title, review_text, review_date, rating, category, images) VALUES ('未知酒店', '未知地点', '匿名', '一家很有故事的酒店', '一家很有故事的酒店
